Definition: white crystalline compound used as a food additive to enhance flavor
Example: often used in Chinese cooking; food manufacturers sometimes list MSG simply as `artificial flavors' in ingredient lists
Synonyms: MSG, flavoring, white, crystalline, compound, used, as, a, food, additive, to, enhance, flavor, often, in, Chinese, cooking, manufacturers, sometimes, list, simply, artificial, flavors, ingredient, lists
Category: noun.food
